Kup(via commlink): I'm in the Commander's office with Yggdrasil, Rodimus, and a few others. Please tell me that you found a cure, Jackie.
 cardhead649 <cardhead649@...> wrote:Wheeljack-X::

After what seems like ages of testing and experiments, Jackie whoops 
in triumph.  He's finally discovered a chemical formula that can 
destroy the rust plague!  He runs a few more tests to make sure, then 
grabs a test tube of the stuff and dashes out the door.

"Kup!  Kup, where are you?" he calls into his comm unit, barely able 
to contain his excitement.
